In [4]:
@tf.function
def preprocess(image, label, augment=True, height=224, width=224):
    image = tf.cast(image, tf.float32)
    image = tf.image.resize_with_crop_or_pad(image, height, width)
    if augment:
        image = tf.image.random_brightness(image, max_delta=0.5)
        image = tf.image.random_flip_left_right(image)
    image = tf.keras.applications.resnet.preprocess_input(image)
    label = tf.one_hot(label, depth=2)
    return image,label



norm_train_ds = train_ds.map(lambda x: (x['image'], x['label']), num_parallel_calls=tf.data.experimental.AUTOTUNE)\
        .map(lambda x,y: preprocess(x,y,augment=True), num_parallel_calls=tf.data.experimental.AUTOTUNE)\
        .shuffle(500).batch(24).prefetch(10)
norm_val_ds = val_ds.map(lambda x: (x['image'], x['label']), num_parallel_calls=tf.data.experimental.AUTOTUNE)\
        .map(lambda x,y: preprocess(x,y,augment=False), num_parallel_calls=tf.data.experimental.AUTOTUNE)\
        .batch(24).cache()

In [5]:
input_layer = layers.Input(shape=(224,224,3))

feat_extractor = tf.keras.applications.ResNet50(include_top=False, weights='imagenet', input_tensor=input_layer)
#feat_extractor = tf.keras.applications.VGG16(include_top=False, weights="imagenet", input_tensor=input_layer)
feat_extractor.trainable = False

logits = layers.Flatten()(feat_extractor.output)
x = layers.Dense(1024, 'relu')(logits)
x = layers.Dropout(0.5)(x)
x = layers.Dense(256, 'relu')(x)
x = layers.Dropout(0.5)(x)
x = layers.Dense(2, 'sigmoid')(x)

model = Model(inputs=[input_layer], outputs=[x], name='feature_extractor')
In [6]:
model.compile(optimizer='adam', loss=tf.keras.losses.BinaryCrossentropy(label_smoothing=0.2), metrics=['accuracy'])

date_str = str(datetime.now())
early_stop = callbacks.EarlyStopping(monitor='val_accuracy', min_delta=1e-2, patience=3,
                                     mode='max', restore_best_weights=True)

                                       monitor='val_loss', save_best_only=True)
tboard = callbacks.TensorBoard(f'../../reports/tboard/cat_vs_dogs_{date_str}/')

plt.figure(figsize=(25,25))
grid_size = 8


val_batch = next(norm_val_ds.shuffle(10).__iter__())
pred_batch = model.predict(val_batch)
label = lambda pred: 'dog' if tf.math.argmax(pred)==1 else 'cat'
color = lambda pred, label: 'green' if pred == label else 'red'
mean_imagenet = np.array([123.68, 116.779, 103.939], dtype=np.float32).reshape((1,1,3))


for i, example in enumerate(zip(val_batch[0], pred_batch)):
    example = (tf.reverse(example[0], axis=[-1]).numpy(), example[1])
    plt.subplot(grid_size,grid_size,i+1)
    plt.xticks([])
    plt.yticks([])
    plt.grid(False)
    plt.imshow(np.sum([example[0], mean_imagenet],axis=-1).astype('uint8'), cmap=plt.cm.binary)

    plt.xlabel(f"{label(example[1])} {tf.reduce_max(example[1]):.3f}", color=f'{color(label(example[1]), label(val_batch[1][i].numpy()))}')
